author: Today I Found Out
description:
In the compilation video today, we're looking at things like What Happens to Your Stuff When You Get Sent to Prison for Life? When Did Having a Prisoner's Last Meal Be Anything They Want Start? Why Does the U.S. Have Such an Insanely Large Prison Population? King Con(man) and His Amazing Escapes from Prison. The Insane Real Life 19th Century Rotating Squirrel Cage Human Prison Design. The Soldier Who Voluntarily Became a Prisoner in Auschwitz. From a Life of Crime to One of the Most Prolific Actors of All Time- Danny Trejo's Prison Break.

Host: Simon Whistler
Editor: Daven Hiskey
Authors: Daven Hiskey, Karl Smallwood, Gilles Messier
